<br>
It's certainly not easy, but I wouldn't say you have no time to chat.  During downtime, you put on clarity if your group is caster heavy, or regen if all the group is hurt, and you take a break.  We chat a lot, but we chat in spurts.  During fights, all our attention is on the fight.  Between fights, we heal and crack our group up, and re-think our current song selection..<br>
<br>
What you call work I call action.  Targetting a mob and hitting the autoattack hotkey, and an occasional combat hotkey is, well, pretty boring to me.  So is sitting and waiting for your mana to get up.  If you like low-intensity play, then this is definately not for you. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=ktadema>ktadema</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://mark.scns.com/eq/givins.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br>  Posts: 121<br> <font color=#ffffff>(4/1/03 6:23:32 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=25537.topic&index=28>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: .</span><hr size=1> An interesting idea for sure!!!!   /applause <p>Givins, 62nd level Erudite Wizard, Rodcet Nife  </p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=syrne>Syrne</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br>  Posts: 335<br> <font color=#ffffff>(4/1/03 11:39:45 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=25537.topic&index=29>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: .</span><hr size=1> I hear bards talk all the time...It usually just has some (quite a few) numbers thrown in at random where they were attempting to twist whilst typing.   <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=behir@graffeswizardcompilation>Behir</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=1